name: Vrainers. The E-Learning of the Future
summary: Train in an emotional, interactive and safe environment! The App allows people to train and learn the Public Speaking, Storytelling and Mindfulness. You will have access to two types of content: theoretical and practical. The theory will be managed by our Virtual Coach, Tony! In the second part, it will be possible to practice in front of a real room of people and test your skills in a realistic and natural environment.
